{
  "texts": [
    "The dataset contains 606 sample images, including 320 Cort, 155 Shsy5y, and 131 Astro samples.The second dataset used in the study is the data science bowl (DSB) dataset [58].",
    "This dataset is one of the popular datasets used in many studies in the literature.",
    "The data consist of images of cell nuclei collected by specialist personnel in various hospitals and universities.",
    "The cell nuclei in the dataset were obtained from mouse, fly, and human cell nuclei.",
    "There are a total of 735 images in the dataset used in the study."
  ]
}